beer.beer_description:
An American IPA with a rounded malt character and a resinous hop profile. Mosaic & Citra hops bring out a pineapple and stonefruit aroma, complemented by the citrus spice of NZ Motueka.

Malts: Pale malt, Victory malt, medium crystal, caramunich, rolled barley

Hops: Magnum, Mosaic, Citra, Motueka
